  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20091227" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">公开的是一种从钻机平台(10)上钻/扩海上或陆上油或气井的装置和方法，它用一个方钻杆(22)转动一个轴向可移动的方钻杆驱动套筒(36)和驱动装置(46-62或46a-62a)以传递转矩给钻杆。马达(26)，方钻杆(22)和方钻杆驱动套筒(36)位于钻杆旋转轴线之外，因此叫做侧传动。这种装置和方法允许用多个钻杆连接在一起进行钻和扩井而不需要用大功率顶部传动马达和大功率电线附件，不需要增加传统井架的高度。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20091227" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>The patent refers to the field of 'methods or apparatus for drilling '. This invention discloses apparatus and a method used for drilling/reaming of offshore or onshore oil or gas wells from a rig platform (10) by using a motor (26) driven rotatable, axially stationary, kelly (22) for rotating an axially moveable kelly driven bushing (36) and drive assembly (46-62) to impart torque to drill pipe 20. The motor (26), kelly (22) and kelly driven bushing (36) are located 32 apart from the drill pipe rotational axis and hence referred to as a side drive. This apparatus and method allows well bore drilling and reaming with 20 multi-connected drill pipe (triples) without heavy duty top drive motors and attendant heavy duty electrical cables, without increasing conventional derrick height thereby facilitating retro-fitting of existing derricks and may be practiced either on floating or stationary platforms.</p>
  </abstract>
